&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Prioritize critically and comfortably adapt to an ever-evolving product landscape&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Operate in ambiguity, making informed decisions even in never-before-seen situations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Partner with engineers, teammates, and other internal stakeholders to diagnose and resolve user issues, both individually and at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Suggest and drive improvements to increase user satisfaction through support processes as well as own initiatives that increase efficiency and drive down contact rates&lt;/li&gt;
